---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog Details | Associum">


    <!-- Header will be injected here -->
    

    <main class="blog-details-container">
        <!-- Content will be injected here via JS -->
        <div id="blog-details-content" class="blog-layout">
            <aside class="blog-sidebar">
                <div class="sidebar-block" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">
                    <span class="sidebar-label">Written By</span>
                    <div class="author-block">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=150&h=150" alt="Jordan Belfort" class="author-avatar">
                        <span class="sidebar-value">Jordan Belfort</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="sidebar-block" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.2s">
                    <span class="sidebar-label">Published On</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-value">May 15, 2026</span>
                </div>
                <div class="sidebar-block" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.3s">
                    <span class="sidebar-label">Reading Time</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-value">4 min read</span>
                </div>
                <div class="sidebar-block" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.4s">
                    <span class="sidebar-label">Overview</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-value">Discover how AI-powered workflows are helping analysts process data faster, generate insights instantly, and reduce manual research tasks by over 60%.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="sidebar-block" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.5s">
                    <span class="sidebar-label">Share</span>
                    <div class="share-links">
                        <a href="https://associum.ai/blog/1" aria-label="Share on LinkedIn"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg></a>
                        <a href="https://associum.ai/blog/1" aria-label="Share on Twitter"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"/></svg></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <article class="blog-article">
                <h1 class="blog-title" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">Most "AI Presentation Tools" Are Slide Decorators. Investment Professionals Need Analytical Generators.</h1>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557683316-973673baf926?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000&h=500" alt="Most AI Presentation Tools Are Slide Decorators" class="blog-hero-image" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.2s">
                <div class="blog-html-content" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.3s">
                    <p>In a world where AI tools are rapidly becoming part of everyday workflows, most platforms struggle to address the specific needs of professional services firms. From investment research to compliance tracking, generic tools simply don't cut it.</p>
                    <h2>What current tools actually do</h2>
                    <p>They act primarily as decorators, making existing slides look slightly better without adding analytical depth or new insights. Most AI presentation tools focus on aesthetics — template selection, color matching, and layout adjustments — while completely ignoring the analytical rigor that investment professionals demand.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Format existing text with minimal intelligence</li>
                        <li>Add basic templates that lack industry specificity</li>
                        <li>Lack real data integration and sourcing</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h2>What an analytical generator does</h2>
                    <p>An analytical generator doesn't just arrange your slides — it builds them from data. It processes raw financial information, identifies patterns, constructs narratives backed by evidence, and presents them in a format that investment committees actually want to see.</p>
                    <h3>1. Prompt to analytical check, fully customizable</h3>
                    <p>You can define exactly what you want the tool to analyze — from cash flow projections to market comparables — and it works flawlessly within seconds, delivering structured outputs ready for presentation.</p>
                    <h3>2. Any amount of data</h3>
                    <p>Ingest massive financial datasets, earnings transcripts, and research reports without hitting token limits. The platform scales with your data needs, not against them.</p>
                    <h3>3. Finishing happens inside the platform</h3>
                    <p>No need to export to PowerPoint just to make the final tweaks. Everything from data visualization to narrative refinement happens in one unified workspace.</p>
                    <h2>What this looks like in practice</h2>
                    <p>Imagine uploading a company's last four quarterly reports along with industry benchmarks. Within minutes, you have a complete investment thesis presentation with supporting charts, risk assessments, and peer comparisons — all sourced and cited.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>

        <!-- Related Articles Section -->
        <section id="related-articles" class="related-articles-section" aria-label="Related Articles">
            <h2 class="related-articles-title" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">Related Articles</h2>
            <div class="related-articles-grid">
                <div class="related-card" onclick="window.location.href='/blogsdetails'" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000&h=500" alt="How AI Is Transforming Investment Research" class="related-card-image">
                    <div class="related-card-meta">
                        <span class="related-card-date">May 15, 2026</span>
                        <span class="related-card-readtime">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
                                <path d="M7 0C10.8661 0 14 3.1339 14 7C14 10.8661 10.8661 14 7 14C3.1339 14 0 10.8661 0 7C0 3.1339 3.1339 0 7 0ZM7 1.4C5.51479 1.4 4.09041 1.99 3.0402 3.0402C1.99 4.09041 1.4 5.51479 1.4 7C1.4 8.48521 1.99 9.90959 3.0402 10.9598C4.09041 12.01 5.51479 12.6 7 12.6C8.48521 12.6 9.90959 12.01 10.9598 10.9598C12.01 9.90959 12.6 8.48521 12.6 7C12.6 5.51479 12.01 4.09041 10.9598 3.0402C9.90959 1.99 8.48521 1.4 7 1.4ZM7 2.8C7.17145 2.80002 7.33694 2.86297 7.46506 2.9769C7.59318 3.09083 7.67504 3.24782 7.6951 3.4181L7.7 3.5V6.7102L9.5949 8.6051C9.72044 8.73107 9.79333 8.9001 9.79876 9.07787C9.80419 9.25563 9.74175 9.4288 9.62413 9.56219C9.5065 9.69559 9.34251 9.77921 9.16547 9.79608C8.98842 9.81294 8.81159 9.76179 8.6709 9.653L8.6051 9.5949L6.5051 7.4949C6.3963 7.38601 6.32643 7.2443 6.3063 7.0917L6.3 7V3.5C6.3 3.31435 6.37375 3.1363 6.50503 3.00503C6.6363 2.87375 6.81435 2.8 7 2.8Z" fill="#888E9E"/>
                            </svg>
                            4 min read
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="related-card-title">How AI Is Transforming Investment Research</h3>
                    <p class="related-card-excerpt">Discover how AI-powered workflows are helping analysts process data faster, generate insights instantly, and reduce manual research tasks by over 60%.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="related-card" onclick="window.location.href='/blogsdetails'" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.2s">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000&h=500" alt="The Future of Due Diligence in Private Equity" class="related-card-image">
                    <div class="related-card-meta">
                        <span class="related-card-date">May 15, 2026</span>
                        <span class="related-card-readtime">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
                                <path d="M7 0C10.8661 0 14 3.1339 14 7C14 10.8661 10.8661 14 7 14C3.1339 14 0 10.8661 0 7C0 3.1339 3.1339 0 7 0ZM7 1.4C5.51479 1.4 4.09041 1.99 3.0402 3.0402C1.99 4.09041 1.4 5.51479 1.4 7C1.4 8.48521 1.99 9.90959 3.0402 10.9598C4.09041 12.01 5.51479 12.6 7 12.6C8.48521 12.6 9.90959 12.01 10.9598 10.9598C12.01 9.90959 12.6 8.48521 12.6 7C12.6 5.51479 12.01 4.09041 10.9598 3.0402C9.90959 1.99 8.48521 1.4 7 1.4ZM7 2.8C7.17145 2.80002 7.33694 2.86297 7.46506 2.9769C7.59318 3.09083 7.67504 3.24782 7.6951 3.4181L7.7 3.5V6.7102L9.5949 8.6051C9.72044 8.73107 9.79333 8.9001 9.79876 9.07787C9.80419 9.25563 9.74175 9.4288 9.62413 9.56219C9.5065 9.69559 9.34251 9.77921 9.16547 9.79608C8.98842 9.81294 8.81159 9.76179 8.6709 9.653L8.6051 9.5949L6.5051 7.4949C6.3963 7.38601 6.32643 7.2443 6.3063 7.0917L6.3 7V3.5C6.3 3.31435 6.37375 3.1363 6.50503 3.00503C6.6363 2.87375 6.81435 2.8 7 2.8Z" fill="#888E9E"/>
                            </svg>
                            4 min read
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="related-card-title">The Future of Due Diligence in Private Equity</h3>
                    <p class="related-card-excerpt">Explore how modern deal teams are automating diligence processes, organizing data rooms, and accelerating investment decisions.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="related-card" onclick="window.location.href='/blogsdetails'" data-reveal="true" style="--reveal-delay: 0.3s">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-8d04cb21cd6c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000&h=500" alt="Why Research Teams Need a Centralized Knowledge Base" class="related-card-image">
                    <div class="related-card-meta">
                        <span class="related-card-date">May 15, 2026</span>
                        <span class="related-card-readtime">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
                                <path d="M7 0C10.8661 0 14 3.1339 14 7C14 10.8661 10.8661 14 7 14C3.1339 14 0 10.8661 0 7C0 3.1339 3.1339 0 7 0ZM7 1.4C5.51479 1.4 4.09041 1.99 3.0402 3.0402C1.99 4.09041 1.4 5.51479 1.4 7C1.4 8.48521 1.99 9.90959 3.0402 10.9598C4.09041 12.01 5.51479 12.6 7 12.6C8.48521 12.6 9.90959 12.01 10.9598 10.9598C12.01 9.90959 12.6 8.48521 12.6 7C12.6 5.51479 12.01 4.09041 10.9598 3.0402C9.90959 1.99 8.48521 1.4 7 1.4ZM7 2.8C7.17145 2.80002 7.33694 2.86297 7.46506 2.9769C7.59318 3.09083 7.67504 3.24782 7.6951 3.4181L7.7 3.5V6.7102L9.5949 8.6051C9.72044 8.73107 9.79333 8.9001 9.79876 9.07787C9.80419 9.25563 9.74175 9.4288 9.62413 9.56219C9.5065 9.69559 9.34251 9.77921 9.16547 9.79608C8.98842 9.81294 8.81159 9.76179 8.6709 9.653L8.6051 9.5949L6.5051 7.4949C6.3963 7.38601 6.32643 7.2443 6.3063 7.0917L6.3 7V3.5C6.3 3.31435 6.37375 3.1363 6.50503 3.00503C6.6363 2.87375 6.81435 2.8 7 2.8Z" fill="#888E9E"/>
                            </svg>
                            4 min read
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="related-card-title">Why Research Teams Need a Centralized Knowledge Base</h3>
                    <p class="related-card-excerpt">Learn how firms can retain institutional knowledge, surface past analysis, and improve collaboration across teams.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer will be injected here -->
    <footer id="footer-placeholder"></footer>

    <!-- Component Loader Script -->
    
    

</Layout>

<style>
.blog-details-container {
    background: #FFF;
    width: 100%;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    /* Base padding */
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

.blog-layout {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 180px 100px 100px 100px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
    /* for sticky to work correctly */
}

/* Sidebar */
.blog-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
}

.sidebar-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
}

.sidebar-label {
    color: var(--Text-Teritiary, #888E9E);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.sidebar-value {
    color: var(--Text-Primary, #0F0F10);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 150%;
}

.author-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
}

.author-avatar {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
}

.share-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
}

.share-links a {
    color: var(--Text-Secondary, #323741);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
}

.share-links a:hover {
    color: #059466;
}

/* Article Main */
.blog-article {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
    width: 100%;
    min-width: 0;
}

.blog-title {
    color: var(--Text-Primary, #0F0F10);
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 120%;
    margin: 0;
}

.blog-hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 500px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
}

.blog-html-content {
    color: var(--Text-Secondary, #323741);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 160%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
}

.blog-html-content h2,
.blog-html-content h3 {
    color: var(--Text-Primary, #0F0F10);
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.blog-html-content p {
    margin: 0;
}

.blog-html-content ul,
.blog-html-content ol {
    margin-left: 20px;
    padding: 0;
}

.blog-html-content li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

/* Not Found fallback */
.blog-not-found {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px;
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
}

.blog-not-found h1 {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    color: #0F0F10;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.blog-not-found p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: #888E9E;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.back-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: #059466;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
}

.back-button:hover {
    background: #047A54;
}

/* Related Articles Section */
.related-articles-section {
    display: flex;
    padding: 60px 100px 100px 100px;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 60px;
    align-self: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--Neutral-200, #EAEDF2);
}

.related-articles-title {
    color: var(--Text-Primary, #0F0F10);
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 130%;
    margin: 0 0 40px 0;
}

.related-articles-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
}

.related-articles-grid::after {
    content: '';
    padding-right: 20px; /* Ensures trailing space on mobile scroll */
}

.related-articles-grid::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
}

.related-card {
    flex: 0 0 calc(33.333% - 16px);
    min-width: 280px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    cursor: pointer;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.related-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
}

.related-card-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
}

.related-card-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px 0 8px 0;
}

.related-card-date {
    color: var(--Text-Teritiary, #888E9E);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
}

.related-card-readtime {
    color: var(--Text-Teritiary, #888E9E);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
}

.related-card-title {
    color: var(--Text-Primary, #0F0F10);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 140%;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.related-card-excerpt {
    color: var(--Text-Secondary, #323741);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 150%;
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin: 0;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
}

/* Responsive Styles */
@media screen and (max-width: 1023px) {
    .blog-details-container {
        padding-top: 80px;
    }

    .blog-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
        padding: 100px 20px 80px 20px;
    }

    .blog-sidebar {
        position: static;
        flex-direction: row;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 24px;
        align-items: flex-start;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--Neutral-200, #EAEDF2);
        padding-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .sidebar-block {
        flex: 1 1 200px;
        /* Allow wrapping */
    }

    .blog-title {
        font-size: 36px;
    }

    .related-card {
        flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 12px);
        min-width: 260px;
    }

    .related-articles-title {
        font-size: 28px;
    }
}

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
    .blog-details-container {
        padding-top: 40px;
    }

    .blog-title {
        font-size: 32px;
    }

    .blog-sidebar {
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .sidebar-block {
        flex: 1 1 auto;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .blog-html-content {
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .blog-hero-image {
        max-height: 300px;
    }

    .related-articles-section {
        padding: 40px 0 0 0;
    }

    .related-card {
        flex: 0 0 100%;
        min-width: unset;
    }

    .related-articles-title {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
}


@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .blog-layout {
        padding: 180px 20px 80px 20px;
    }

    .blog-title {
        font-size: 36px;
    }

    .related-articles-section {
        padding: 80px 40px 80px 40px;
        gap: 40px;
    }

    .related-articles-title {
        margin: 0px;
    }
}


@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-title {
        font-size: 32px;
    }

    .blog-layout {
        padding: 100px 20px 80px 20px;
    }

    .related-articles-section {
        padding: 20px;
        gap: 30px;
    }

    .related-card {
        flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 12px);
        min-width: 220px;
    }

    .related-articles-section {
        padding: 80px 20px;
        gap: 30px;
    }

}


@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {

    .blog-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .blog-html-content {
        gap: 20px;
    }

    /* Fix horizontal scroll cut-off and add full bleed effect */
    .related-articles-section {
        padding-left: 0 !important;
        padding-right: 0 !important;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .related-articles-title {
        padding-left: 20px;
        padding-right: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .related-articles-grid {
        padding-left: 20px;
        padding-right: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .related-articles-grid::after {
        content: '';
        flex: 0 0 20px; /* Force 20px trailing space */
    }
}
</style>

<script is:inline>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => { if (typeof window.initScrollReveal === 'function') { window.initScrollReveal(); } });

</script>
